title: Caramel Coconut Crave S'more
description:
Camp Chef S'more of the  Week | Caramel Coconut Crave

This is no ordinary s'more. You will crave more than just one. Make sure you get plenty of ingredients and be prepared to sit by the fire for a while because the Caramel Coconut Crave S'more...one just won't be enough.

Ingredients:

• Toasted Coconut
• Caramel
• Chocolate
• Marshmallow
• Graham
